The paper focuses on learning numerical representations of text values in databases, which suggests a strong connection to the field of database systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of word embeddings, which are commonly used in natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as text classification (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also presents an algorithm for solving a learning problem, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
